OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry start, with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. However, cloud soon thickening
OL,7,Ffrom the west, with winds also
OL,8,Fstrengthening. Likely staying dry
OL,9,Funtil after dark.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain and drizzle spreading
OL,12,Feast, to become widespread overnight.
OL,13,FThis mostly light but with some
OL,14,Fheavier bursts possible, but perhaps
OL,15,Fthe odd drier spell developing towards
OL,16,Fdawn. Winds easing. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
